search_workflow.narrative: search all cathedral with the respective country
search_workflow.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?ch ?coname WHERE { ?ch wdt:P31 wd:Q2977. ?ch wdt:P17 ?co. ?co <http://schema.org/name> ?coname } LIMIT 50
SELECT DISTINCT (COUNT(?ch) AS ?howManyChatedrals) ?coname WHERE { ?ch wdt:P31 wd:Q2977. ?ch wdt:P17 ?co. ?co <http://schema.org/name> ?coname } GROUP BY ?coname LIMIT 100

search_workflow.narrative: select the country with more cathedrals
search_workflow.query: SELECT DISTINCT (COUNT(?ch) AS ?howManyChatedrals) ?coname WHERE { ?ch wdt:P31 wd:Q2977. ?ch wdt:P17 ?co. ?co <http://schema.org/name> ?coname } GROUP BY ?coname ORDER BY DESC (COUNT(?ch)) LIMIT 1

SELECT ?country ?style (COUNT(?ch) AS ?howManyChatedrals) WHERE { ?ch wdt:P31 wd:Q2977. ?ch wdt:P17 ?co. ?ch wdt:P149 ?s. ?co <http://schema.org/name> ?country. ?s <http://schema.org/name> ?style. } GROUP BY ?country ?style LIMIT 100
SELECT ?cname ?area WHERE { ?ch wdt:P31 wd:Q2977. ?ch wdt:P2046 ?area. ?ch <http://schema.org/name> ?cname. } ORDER BY DESC (?area) LIMIT 1
SELECT ?cname ?date WHERE { ?ch wdt:P31 wd:Q2977. ?ch wdt:P1619 ?date. ?ch <http://schema.org/name> ?cname } ORDER BY ASC (?date) LIMIT 1

search_workflow.narrative: city with the highest number of cathedral
search_workflow.query: SELECT (COUNT(?cname) AS ?howmanycathedral) ?cityname WHERE { ?ch wdt:P31 wd:Q2977. ?ch wdt:P276 ?city. ?ch <http://schema.org/name> ?cname. ?city <http://schema.org/name> ?cityname. } GROUP BY ?cityname ORDER BY DESC (?howmanycathedral) LIMIT 1
